      <scopecontent>
         <p>The bulk of the collection contains correspondences and financial files. The photographs of rugs and research related materials are contained in Hubbell Trading Post series. The documents from different committees are organized by committees and arranged alphabetically in SPMA series. The meeting minutes and agenda and publication are included in SPMA as well. </p>
      </scopecontent>
